The simulation results for the corona virus-load are presented in Fig. 5, Fig. 6, and Fig. 7. Based on these figures, by giving 100 the corona virus-load, the COVID-19 outbreak will never vanish in the population, and the recovery rate tends to remain, but it is smaller than those infected with COVID-19. Meanwhile, if the virus corona-load is 50, the epidemic tends to decrease, and if \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
